   "source": [
    "What is the $2 \\times 2$ matrix $A$ that produces this transformation?\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.callout-tip collapse=\"true\"}\n",
    "## Solution\n",
    "\n",
    "The columns of $A$ are the images of the basis vectors. $(1, 0)$ goes to $(3, -1)$ and $(0, 1)$ goes to $(2, 3)$:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$A = \\begin{bmatrix} 3 & 2 \\\\ -1 & 3 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Verify: $A \\begin{bmatrix} 1 \\\\ 1 \\end{bmatrix} = \\begin{bmatrix} 5 \\\\ 2 \\end{bmatrix}$ ✓\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "### Interactive Tool: Linear Transformations\n",
    "\n",
    "::: {.callout-note}\n",
    "This is an interactive tool to develop your understanding of the material. You can change the values in the fields below or adjust positions of the vectors on the plots to visualize various linear transformations. You can also look at some pre-determined transformations from the drop-down menu.\n",
    ":::\n",
    "\n",
    "```{ojs}\n",
    "//| echo: false\n",
    "\n",
    "// ── Presets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "\n",
    "presets = new Map([\n",
    "  [\"Identity\",            {a:1,  b:0,  c:0,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Scale (2, 1)\",        {a:2,  b:0,  c:0,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Scale (1, 2)\",        {a:1,  b:0,  c:0,  d:2}],\n",
    "  [\"Scale (2, 2)\",        {a:2,  b:0,  c:0,  d:2}],\n",
    "  [\"Rotation 45°\",        {a:Math.cos(Math.PI/4), b:-Math.sin(Math.PI/4),\n",
    "                           c:Math.sin(Math.PI/4), d: Math.cos(Math.PI/4)}],\n",
    "  [\"Rotation 90°\",        {a:0,  b:-1, c:1,  d:0}],\n",
    "  [\"Rotation 180°\",       {a:-1, b:0,  c:0,  d:-1}],\n",
    "  [\"Reflection (a-axis)\",  {a:1,  b:0,  c:0,  d:-1}],\n",
    "  [\"Reflection (b-axis)\",  {a:-1, b:0,  c:0,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Reflection (a=b)\",    {a:0,  b:1,  c:1,  d:0}],\n",
    "  [\"Shear horizontal\",    {a:1,  b:1,  c:0,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Shear vertical\",      {a:1,  b:0,  c:1,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Projection onto a\",   {a:1,  b:0,  c:0,  d:0}],\n",
    "  [\"Projection onto b\",   {a:0,  b:0,  c:0,  d:1}],\n",
    "  [\"Squeeze\",             {a:2,  b:0,  c:0,  d:0.5}],\n",
    "])\n",
    "\n",
    "round4 = (x) => Math.round(x * 10000) / 10000\n",
    "```\n",
